data.value: SELECT T0."CardName", T0."CardCode" FROM OCRD T0 INNER JOIN "@UBP1" T1 ON T1."U_GroupCode" = T0."GroupCode" INNER JOIN "@OUBP" T2 ON T2."Code" = T1."Code" WHERE T2."U_User" = (SELECT "USER_CODE" FROM OUSR WHERE "INTERNAL_K" = $[USER])
data.comment: Get list of Business Partners by User (Customer and Vendor Name)

data.name: QRY_BPNameVendorByUser
data.value: SELECT T0."CardName", T0."CardCode" FROM OCRD T0 INNER JOIN "@UBP1" T1 ON T1."U_GroupCode" = T0."GroupCode" INNER JOIN "@OUBP" T2 ON T2."Code" = T1."Code" WHERE T0."CardType" = 'S' AND T2."U_User" = (SELECT "USER_CODE" FROM OUSR WHERE "INTERNAL_K" = $[USER])
data.comment: Get list of Business Partners by User (Vendor Name)

data.name: QRY_BPVendorByUser
data.value: SELECT T0."CardCode", T0."CardName" FROM OCRD T0 INNER JOIN "@UBP1" T1 ON T1."U_GroupCode" = T0."GroupCode" INNER JOIN "@OUBP" T2 ON T2."Code" = T1."Code" WHERE T0."CardType" = 'S' AND T2."U_User" = (SELECT "USER_CODE" FROM OUSR WHERE "INTERNAL_K" = $[USER])
data.comment: Get list of Business Partners by User (Vendor Code)

data.name: QRY_COAByUser
data.value: SELECT T1."U_AccountCode", T2."AcctName" FROM "@OUAC" T0 JOIN "@UAC1" T1 ON T0."Code" = T1."Code" JOIN "OACT" T2 ON T1."U_AccountCode" = T2."AcctCode" WHERE T0."U_User" = (SELECT "USER_CODE" FROM OUSR WHERE "INTERNAL_K" = $[USER])
data.comment: Get list of Accounts by current user

data.name: QRY_AllAccounts
data.value: SELECT "AcctCode", "AcctName" FROM OACT
data.comment: Get list of All Accounts

data.name: QRY_AllProjectsName
data.value: SELECT T0."PrjName", T0."PrjCode" FROM OPRJ T0
data.comment: Get list of All Project Names in SAP
